(d) Your boss really likes the new allocation strategy but he is concerned
 that it may incur high monthly transaction costs, which have not been incorpora
ted in the Markowitz theory and its extensions.
 Define portfolio turnover rate at period 
\begin_inset Formula $t+1$
\end_inset

 as
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
TR(t+1)=\frac{\sum_{i=1}^{6}|P_{i,t+1}-P_{i,t}|}{\sum_{i=1}^{6}|P_{i,t+1}|},
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $P_{i,t}$
\end_inset

 is the dollar amount invested in the 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

th Fama-French portfolio in period 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

.
